<p>This form of split-hand/foot malformation with long bone deficiency (SHFLD1) maps to chromosome 1q42.2-q43.</p>

<p>See also SHFLD2, which maps to chromosome 6q14.1, and SHFLD3, which maps to chromosome 17p13.3-p13.1. Split-hand/foot malformation with fibular hypoplasia/aplasia has also been reported, see.</p>